    <tal:block metal:fill-slot="content_body">
        <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row-fluid">    
           
        <div class="span9">    
        <h2>Brief introduction</h2>
        <p>
        Connect is a <em>connect(m, n, 6, 2, 1)</em> game, also called <em>Connect6</em>,
        a revised version of Gomoku. The rules are very simple,
        the game starts with the black player placing one stone on the board, subsequently white and black player
        take turns placing two stones of their respective colors on the board. 
        The winner is the player who is the first to get six stones of his color in a row (horizontally, vertically, diagonally).
        </div>
        </div>
        </div>
